This is not the ordinary heroes movie you will see, this is more than that! really! 2 and half hours feel like minutes! every scene is perfect, soundtrack composing is neat and they did not add unnecessary sounds. Narratives is way too perfect composed. The story flows like a river in the spring, no plot hole. Interesting twist. and this is really original story but did not lose the real origin story of the comic version. Many old comic references (I spotted almost every scenes referring to the comic and Alex Ross drawing!). However, one thing that disappoint me is (SPOILER) Ares costume is sooooo simple! Where is the cape, the dreadful mask and where is his black aura? bruh, the CGI is way too simple. but overall, THIS IS THE BEST DC COMIC MOVIE SO FAR! I cannot wait for Justice League this November! and I will for sure will rewatch this in the near future. Gal Gadot is soooo beautiful and perfectly portrait Wonder Woman!
